'''Siatta Scott Johnson''' ( yavutse 1974), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo [[Liberiya|muri Liberiya]] akaba n'umunyamakuru utangaza amakuru.  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa documentaire izwi cyane ''Iron Ladies of Liberia'' .  Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, ni umunyamakuru ndetse na  producer. Ni n'umunyamuryango washinze itangazamakuru rya Omuahtee Africa. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1974 i Buchanan, muri [[Liberiya]]. Nyuma yakuriye mu cyaro cya Grand Bassa . Mu ntangiriro ya za 90, Johnson yahunze avuye muri Grand Bassa intambara itangira. Nyuma yaje gutura muri Monrovia mu gihe intambara yarangiraga mu 2003. 

Amashuri amaze gufungura nyuma y'intambara, Johnson yarangije icyiciro cya kabiri cya Bachelor of Arts mu itumanaho rusange yakuye muri kaminuza ya Liberiya .  Hanyuma, yafashe impamyabumenyi muri raporo za politiki yakuye muri kaminuza ya [[Liberiya]], nyuma mu bitangazamakuru avuye mu ihuriro ry’abanyamakuru bo muri Liberiya ndetse n’ubutumwa bw’umuryango w’abibumbye muri Liberiya (UNMIL).  Afite kandi impamyabumenyi mu itangazamakuru yakuye muri Liberia Institute of Journalism. Yakoze kandi nk'umunyamakuru akaba na producer muri Downtown Community Televiziyo Centre (DCTV). 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2007, yakoze documentaire yamamaye cyane ''Iron Ladies yo muri [[Liberiya]]'' afatanije na Daniel Junge.  Iyi documentaire yahawe icyubahiro mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Dallas, Target Ten Filmmaker nka Documentaire nziza yuwo mwaka kandi ibaye Filime Nziza Yaturutse Isi Y’Amashuri mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime Isi ryabereye i Prague. Usibye ibyo, film yanagaragaye mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  

Usibye sinema, ni umunyamakuru uzwi cyane muri [[Liberiya]] aho yakoranye n'ishyirahamwe ry'abanyamakuru b'abagore bo muri [[Liberiya]] (FeJAL).  Yakoze kandi muri Beyondmedia Education i Chicago, muri [[Amerika]]. Johnson amaze gusubira muri [[Liberiya]], yakoze mu kubaka itangazamakuru ry’urubyiruko rwo muri [[Liberiya]].  Nyuma yaje gukora ubuvugizi bw'itangazamakuru mu nama ishinzwe impunzi muri Noruveje (NRC) aho yateguye ibiganiro bya radiyo ku bagore bo mu cyaro mu mushinga witwa “ABAGORE B'UBWENGE”. Yakoranye kandi na Medica Mondiale Liberia nk'ushinzwe itumanaho aho yorohereza impinduka mu myitwarire mu bagore bo mu cyaro batuye mu majyepfo y'uburasirazuba bwa [[Liberiya]]. Johnson yabaye producer wa gahunda ya tereviziyo yitwa 'Amajwi Yingenzi' yari gahunda kubakobwa b'ingimbi n'abangavu. 

Muri 2012, yabaye umuyobozi mukuru n’umuyobozi uhanga muri Smart Media Liberia.  Muri 2019, yongeye gutorerwa kuba perezida w'ishyirahamwe ry'abanyamakuru b'abagore bo muri [[Liberiya]].  

